🏥 HealthCare Management System RESTful API

Welcome to the HealthCare Management System RESTful API — a secure and scalable backend built using Java, Spring Boot,Docker, Redis, Stripe, JWT or Json web Token, OAuth2, Firebase, Spring Security, and MongoDB.
This API provides a complete backend solution for managing hospitals, pharmacies, patients, payments, telemedicine, and more.

